    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for daily commuting. Mechanically, the car is solid; the engine starts up without issue and the transmission shifts through gears as expected, though it lacks the crispness of a newer model. While the car is safe and functional, prospective buyers should note some cosmetic wear on the interior upholstery and a few minor scratches on the exterior body. It has been maintained regularly, but it is not in showroom condition. This is a practical choice for someone prioritizing utility and dependability over perfect aesthetics.",
