    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project? This car is ready for someone with a vision! While it's in poor condition and will require some dedicated mechanical work and TLC to get back in top shape, it presents a fantastic opportunity to own a vehicle at a budget-friendly price. It's an honest start for your next automotive adventure!",
